Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:01:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The commodore seems sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:02:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Just after he made such a\Ngreat friend all the way out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of this makes any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We set sail first thing tomorrow morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the villagers are so\Nbloodthirsty we can't go near 'em,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not to mention, the bell\Ndidn't ring again today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't show your face around me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want your wife to end up a widow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eternal Friends! The Vowed Bell\NEchoes Across the Mighty Seas!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a heartrending way to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mousse-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Botanist, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If these are the victims\Nof your "advancements,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then we should never have accepted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kindred Trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that all the spirits of our\Nancestors who died on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are guided to them by the bell\Nso they can settle inside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of our ancestors who lived on\Nthe island since the age of Shandora
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,watch over us from those sacred, white trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kindred Woods are so\Ntruly important to us Shandians
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we've protected them as much\Nas we've protected our own lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we chopped them all down...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The warriors were angry and\Ninstantly took up their weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We must drive them off this island!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but since you had saved so\Nmany of the villagers' lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that attitude was\Nanger they couldn't act on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was just for tree research...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The villagers' anger won't go away now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I thought I would at least ask why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before you left...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Someone help with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Trees where ancestors' spirits dwell...\N--Get it all on board now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea. We've done something\Nthat can never be taken back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The villagers are right to be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Commodore! We had no choice, given--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No excuses! I only did what satisfied me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told that aside from\Nproclaiming the city's existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that bell also served to guide\Ntheir ancestors' spirits to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we cut down those trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no reason to be forgiven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commodore...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Leave all the gold behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noland and his men are preparing to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mousse! Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you knew a single, important\Ntree was tainted by poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that its poison would\Neventually spread into the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,affect people, and kill an island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you knew beforehand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What are you talking about?!\N--What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would we do with\Nthat single, important tree?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Go quickly and stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a fool! You know what they've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we part now, we'll regret it\Nfor the rest of our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally made such a dear friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we Shandians owe them so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're going to leave them\Nhurt for the rest of their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably sound like an excuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for the commodore's honor, I must say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those woods of yours were already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The true horror of the Kinetsu plague\Nis that it can also infect plant life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because he knew this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the commodore pleaded with\Nyou without regard for his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From people to forest, forest to people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Several small islands have been\Ndestroyed in exactly that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's nothing to worry about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finished checking\Nthe entire forest yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that we cut\Ndown your beloved woods
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without knowing or explaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd probably still be unforgivable\Neven with an explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a botanist would never harm\Na forest without good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The commodore doesn't hate\Ngods and spirits and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that he always\Nknows what's most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means... they did it for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone have everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All except one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit mopin'! Just forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It's time to go!\NEveryone to your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're now heading back\Nto the Lvneel Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've committed such a sin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the bell ringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Noland-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louder! So Noland and the others can hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commodore! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calgara...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noland...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep on ringing the bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that your ship won't get\Nlost at sea when you return...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that you won't lose sight\Nof this island during a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ring this bell and wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again someday\Nfor sure! Friend of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can... come back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'll be back! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again someday for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There once was a man\Nnamed Montblanc Noland,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:44.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"North Blue-- Lvneel Kingdom"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from a kingdom in the northern seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noland the Explorer always told\Nstories of incredible adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the villagers could never\Ntell if they were true or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, Noland returned from a\Njourney and reported to the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stands all the more\Nproudly and beautifully in ruin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This city is named Shandora! The term\N"city of gold" fits it like none other!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:18.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Five Years Later"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marie Jois has finally granted us\Npermission to enter the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, I wish to send\Nyou on another mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it would be my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I've decided my soldiers will\Njoin you on this journey, as will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Understood?\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:39.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"One Year Before Noland's Arrival"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Calgara!\N--Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're off to ring the bell, right? I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nola. You've sure settled into these ruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:13:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say! When do you suppose\NNoland-san and the others will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you ever ask when you come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be so easy for him to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was born in the far northern seas.\NHe also has a family back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he did promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we keep ringing this\Nbell here, he'll show up sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?! This looks bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Seto! We have to protect the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does the island suddenly end here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! You lied to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this gold of yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the village go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calgara! If you're alive, let me hear it!\NThe sound of the gold bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, fire of Shandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noland's public execution's about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This way, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a giant city of gold on\Nthe Grand Line island of Jaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of gold does exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's hear from one of your crewmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this man telling the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's an absolute lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Noland-san is a liar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then were all his stories fake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's messed up! He lied to the\Nwhole kingdom and acted like a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that witness?!\NHe's not part of our crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Calgara and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commodore! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For his heinous lies, Montblanc\NNoland is hereby sentenced
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to death by beheading!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Liar!\N--He's a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The commodore'd never lie!\N--Commodore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! Liar! Liar! Liar!...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God! It's a giant island of Vearth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Did you hear that? The singing\Nvoice of this beautiful Vearth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is truly the birth of holy land.\NThat is where I must live!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! I can't breathe well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is everyone all right?!\N--Pull yourselves together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Pull yourselves together!\N--Tend to the wounded! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calgara! Intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby claim this Vearth as mine! I am God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop them, warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot let this land be taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made a promise, Noland...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That we would meet again someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calgara... Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you return to Jaya, what will\Nyou think when you see we're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a little longer! I'll let\Nyou know that "we are here"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have so much to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calgara...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only concerned for your well-being...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again on the\Nsame land someday, Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fire of Shandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Warrior Calgara continued to shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just once would've been enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For he believed the fire of Shandora\Nwould echo and let all know that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We are here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the bell never once rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was later told to our\Nvillage by sailors from the Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noland, to whom we owe so much,\Nhad such pride for our city
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he refused to deny Shandora's\Nexistence and died known as a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was already too late,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for Great Warrior Calgara had died\Nhonorably in battle here in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never being able to convey his message...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Great Warrior Calgara's greatest regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it could still reach him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bell! If we rang it now,\Nwould its sound reach Noland?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are close to Heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper! We'll die if we don't escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives you the right\Nto take everything away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the sky! God's domain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is an eyesore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people, the trees, the land!\NReturn to where you belong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let everything rain into the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Island won't last much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of injured people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get them into boats, then give them first aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry, into the ocean!\N--Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get chills when I imagine that\Ngirl's speech being any later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's far above now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time until\Nhis ship reaches the top of the vine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it Eneru wants there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gold bell at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scurrying angels are like a\Nline of ants that's been disturbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to where you belong, Skypiea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hole in the White-White Sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need for good\Nold God's Shrine either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor for the city of Shandora below it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is but one thing left\Nin this land that I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The golden grand belfry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two voices, at this final stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! How can he run so fast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't let you have\Nthe golden bell, Eneru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling lonely, talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gaze at the heavens\Nas you wander about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the moon,\Nyou keep your gaze constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your deep reflection wanes\Nas you slowly disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are, let those words guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream, you travelers who spend\Ncountless nights drifting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you may not be able to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will surely start moving forward again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then! Time for that eyesore\Nof an island to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.88,0:23:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! The clouds are changing shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have your way, Eneru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no stopping this Raigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.23,0:23:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to escape, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can just catch him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Angel Island Obliterated!\NThe Horror of the Raigo's Advent!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
[Events]
